data.name: Lune Network
data.description: Welcome to Lune, the ultimate Minecraft server where factions and community collide! Whether you're a Java Edition veteran or an eager Eaglercraft adventurer, Lune welcomes you to a vibrant world of competitive gameplay, strategic alliances, and endless fun. Build your base, form powerful factions, and conquer your rivals in a dynamic environment designed for both casual players and seasoned veterans. Join Lune today and experience the thrill of faction warfare like never before!
